      <title>Separate BASH and KICK</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=warriorbalance&amp;message.id=25768#M25768</link>
      <description>I have played with a shield quite often as a 70 warrior and like the way it ads a new element to game play. It helps alot when the healer is having a hard time landing heals. The problem jumps in when the dps are drawing my aggro alot due to my lack of attacks. I noticed that BASH will remove one of my attacks because I play a dwarf. The larger races never use kick, but I have since day one. The separation of Bash and Kick would allow me three attacks with a shield and I believe would be enough to grant me the ability to hold my aggro and give the healer a better chance to keep me standing while I use the benefits of my shield. This might require separating Bash/Slam too, but I never use Slam anyway.</description>
